in the first place,
I would've lost

255
00:11:02,037 --> 00:11:04,247
all hope for fairness and
justice in this world.

256
00:11:04,289 --> 00:11:06,249
While everybody else was
studying desperately,

257
00:11:06,291 --> 00:11:07,459
he was always sleeping.

258
00:11:07,500 --> 00:11:09,210
On the odd occasions
when he was awake,

259
00:11:09,252 --> 00:11:11,212
he was tooting away
on that flute of his

260
00:11:11,254 --> 00:11:13,214
and to top it all off,
after stuffing his face

