find out for sure.

286
00:12:10,146 --> 00:12:11,940
But then again, he
probably already knows.

287
00:12:11,981 --> 00:12:14,275
- [Eigetsu] Shkrei,
hang in there, okay?

288
00:12:14,317 --> 00:12:17,487
Whatever happens, I'll be
right there by your side.

289
00:12:17,529 --> 00:12:19,989
- Thanks for
reminding me, Eigetsu.

290
00:12:20,031 --> 00:12:22,117
(jazzy music)

291
00:12:22,158 --> 00:12:24,494
(foot steps)

292
00:12:30,166 --> 00:12:31,418
- Secretary Kou.

293
00:12:31,459 --> 00:12:33,461
(gasps)

294
00:12:34,337 --> 00:12:36,965
(jazzy music)

295
00:12:39,050 --> 00:12:41,052
(sighs)

296
00:12:43,430 --> 00:12:45,515
- Senior Secretary,
about last summer.

297
00:12:45,557 --> 00:12:47,308
- [Kijin] What are
you talking about?

298
00:12:47,350 --> 00:12:48,476
- [Shkrei] You don't remember?

299
00:12:48,518 --> 00:12:50,562
I was using the name Shu Hong.

300
00:12:50,603 --> 00:12:52,188
- You must be mistaken.

301
00:12:52,230 --> 00:12:55,025
The Shu Hong I know is a
fairly capable young man.

302
00:12:55,066 --> 00:12:57,068
You would do well to
learn from his example.

303
00:12:57,110 --> 00:12:57,944
- Ah!

304
00:12:58,987 --> 00:13:00,155
Yes.

305
00:13:00,196 --> 00:13:01,322
- By the way, are you
sure it's all right

306
00:13:01,364 --> 00:13:02,949
for you two to be
casually idling

307
00:13:02,991 --> 00:13:04,951
out here at this time of day?

308
00:13:04,993 --> 00:13:05,660
- [Initiates] Huh?

309
00:13:05,702 --> 00:13:06,661
- There you are.

310
00:13:06,703 --> 00:13:07,954
What are you two
doing over here?

311
00:13:07,996 --> 00:13:09,122
You're gonna be late.

312
00:13:09,164 --> 00:13:10,123
- [Initiates] Late?

313
00:13:11,666 --> 00:13:13,168
(gasp)

314
00:13:13,209 --> 00:13:14,419
- [Shkrei] Ah, you
gotta be kidding me.

315
00:13:14,461 --> 00:13:16,171
The meeting time stated
in the letter was wrong?

316
00:13:16,212 --> 00:13:17,672
Gimme a break.

317
00:13:17,714 --> 00:13:19,382
- [Eigetsu] We can't afford
to be late on the first day.

318
00:13:19,424 --> 00:13:21,051
- [Rykki] I can only
imagine it's a prank pulled

319
00:13:21,092 --> 00:13:22,385
by someone jealous of you.

320
00:13:22,427 --> 00:13:24,429
- [Shkrei] We sure
seem to be hated a lot.

321
00:13:24,471 --> 00:13:26,556
- It'll be faster if
we cut through here.

322
00:13:28,224 --> 00:13:30,101
- Geez, I had high
hopes for my future

323
00:13:30,143 --> 00:13:31,519
and then all of this happens.

324
00:13:31,561 --> 00:13:32,896
- That's why I'm here.

325
00:13:32,937 --> 00:13:34,439
For the time being,
most of my duties

326
00:13:34,481 --> 00:13:37,317
as king have been handed over
to a more than capable man.

327
00:13:37,359 --> 00:13:39,361
(groans)

328
00:13:39,402 --> 00:13:40,528
- Huh?

329
00:13:40,570 --> 00:13:43,156
- Starting today,
we, I mean, I will be

330
00:13:43,198 --> 00:13:44,199
your personal guard.

331
00:13:44,240 --> 00:13:46,368
- [Initiates] Huh?

332
00:13:46,409 --> 00:13:48,411
(pants)

333
00:13:49,371 --> 00:13:51,164
- Somehow.

334
00:13:51,206 --> 00:13:52,957
- We were able to
make it in time.

335
00:13:54,292 --> 00:13:56,961
- Hey you two, although it's
a little late to say so,

336
00:13:57,003 --> 00:13:59,130
congratulations on
passing the exams.

337
00:14:00,382 --> 00:14:01,966
- [Eigetsu] Aw, they've wilted.

338
00:14:02,008 --> 00:14:04,094
- I put them in my
pocket right after

339
00:14:04,135 --> 00:14:06,262
I picked them, so, forget it.

340
00:14:06,304 --> 00:14:07,931
- [Shkrei] Oh.

341
00:14:07,972 --> 00:14:09,307
Adonis amurensis.

342
00:14:09,349 --> 00:14:11,976
Congratulatory
flowers, thank you.

343
00:14:12,018 --> 00:14:13,436
Well, we should be going.

344
00:14:22,278 --> 00:14:26,074
{\an8}(traditional Japanese music)

345
00:14:28,493 --> 00:14:31,204
(crowd murmurs)

346
00:14:32,539 --> 00:14:33,581
- [Fellow Initiate] So they
actually came because they

347
00:14:33,623 --> 00:14:35,166
don't know what's good for them.

348
00:14:35,208 --> 00:14:37,377
- [Fellow Initiate] Huh,
a woman taking the exams?

349
00:14:37,419 --> 00:14:38,586
- [Fellow Initiate]
I bet they worried

350
00:14:38,628 --> 00:14:39,796
they'd lose face
if no women passed

351
00:14:39,838 --> 00:14:41,631
so they cut her some
slack and passed her.

352
00:14:41,673 --> 00:14:43,383
- [Fellow Initiate] I was
really thrilled to have passed.

353
00:14:43,425 --> 00:14:44,843
When I heard a woman
did it as well,

354
00:14:44,884 --> 00:14:47,262
it wasn't so special anymore.

355
00:14:47,303 --> 00:14:49,264
- [Fellow Initiate] And
taking the Jougen title at 13?

356
00:14:49,305 --> 00:14:51,349
What trick did he
use to manage that?

357
00:14:51,391 --> 00:14:53,268
- [Fellow Initiate] We've
got a woman and a kid.

358
00:14:53,309 --> 00:14:55,145
This year's a total joke.

359
00:14:55,186 --> 00:14:56,438
- [Initiates] Huh?

360
00:14:56,479 --> 00:14:57,439
- Ah, hmph.

361
00:14:59,315 --> 00:15:01,526
- [Announcer] Senior
Secretary Si and Official Ro

362
00:15:01,568 --> 00:15:04,654
of the Department of
Protocol have arrived.

363
00:15:04,696 --> 00:15:06,489
- I must congratulate you all on

364
00:15:06,531 --> 00:15:08,658
passing the national
examinations.

365
00:15:08,700 --> 00:15:12,162
This year, as per His
Majesty, the top 20 examinees

366
00:15:12,203 --> 00:15:14,873
will be temporarily
assigned to the royal court.

367
00:15:14,914 --> 00:15:16,708
Although it is only
for a short time,

368
00:15:16,750 --> 00:15:19,419
I trust you will all make
the most of the opportunity

369
00:15:19,461 --> 00:15:21,171
and learn as much as you can.

370
00:15:21,212 --> 00:15:23,423
In two months, we will
review your performance

371
00:15:23,465 --> 00:15:25,467
and your formal
placements will be decided

372
00:15:25,508 --> 00:15:27,302
based on your abilities.

373
00:15:27,344 --> 00:15:30,680
Until that time, Official Ro
of the Department of Protocol

374
00:15:30,722 --> 00:15:32,766
will be your instructor.

375
00:15:32,807 --> 00:15:34,642
I'm sure he'll
provide you with all

376
00:15:34,684 --> 00:15:36,186
the guidance you'll need.

377
00:15:36,227 --> 00:15:38,563
(dramatic music)

378
00:15:38,605 --> 00:15:40,857
Just a reminder, they
have yet to be appointed

379
00:15:40,899 --> 00:15:42,567
an official title and rank.

380
00:15:42,609 --> 00:15:44,486
Try not to be too harsh on them.

381
00:15:44,527 --> 00:15:46,321
- Yes, of course, I understand.

382
00:15:46,363 --> 00:15:47,238
- Hmm.

383
00:15:50,367 --> 00:15:52,410
- [Ro] You have managed
to place in the top 20

384
00:15:52,452 --> 00:15:54,871
and are the first new officials
of the present king's reign.

385
00:15:54,913 --> 00:15:56,539
As such, you're
in a good position

386
00:15:56,581 --> 00:15:57,665
to be considered for important

387
00:15:57,707 --> 00:15:59,459
government roles in the future.

388
00:15:59,501 --> 00:16:01,461
Over the next two months,
you will be assigned

389
00:16:01,503 --> 00:16:04,214
various practical jobs
in and around the palace.

390
00:16:04,255 --> 00:16:05,757
After one and a half
months, while you're

391
00:16:05,799 --> 00:16:07,300
still working on
your assignments,

392
00:16:07,342 --> 00:16:08,593
you are to put your
thoughts together

393
00:16:08,635 --> 00:16:10,345
and submit a formal report.

394
00:16:10,387 --> 00:16:13,598
You do not have to submit
this report to me personally.

395
00:16:13,640 --> 00:16:16,768
The content and format
is entirely up to you.

396
00:16:16,810 --> 00:16:18,395
Hm.

397
00:16:18,436 --> 00:16:20,772
Initiate Hong, Initiate Tou,
what is the meaning of this?

398
00:16:20,814 --> 00:16:22,899
Your uniforms are
absolutely filthy.

399
00:16:22,941 --> 00:16:23,942
- Sir, this is--

400
00:16:23,983 --> 00:16:25,610
- Do not talk back, Initiate.

401
00:16:25,652 --> 00:16:27,487
Your appearance is a disgrace.

402
00:16:27,529 --> 00:16:28,905
Were you under the
impression this place

403
00:16:28,947 --> 00:16:30,699
is some chicken coop?

404
00:16:30,740 --> 00:16:32,867
- [Initiates] We're
very sorry, Official Ro.

405
00:16:32,909 --> 00:16:34,786
- It seems you're
lacking self-awareness.

406
00:16:34,828 --> 00:16:36,538
Very well, I'll see
to it that you're

407
00:16:36,579 --> 00:16:38,164
assigned appropriate work.

408
00:16:39,499 --> 00:16:42,252
I will now issue your
designated assignment areas.

409
00:16:42,293 --> 00:16:43,920
For further details
of your duties,

410
00:16:43,962 --> 00:16:46,923
please inquire within
the departments where
you're assigned.

411
00:16:49,634 --> 00:16:52,762
- [Shkrei] (groans) Bring it on!

412
00:16:52,804 --> 00:16:54,639
If they think this is
gonna discourage me,

413
00:16:54,681 --> 00:16:55,890
they're in for a shock.

414
00:16:55,932 --> 00:16:58,309
