00:17:02,689 --> 00:17:04,566
is no different
from the rest of us.

418
00:17:06,860 --> 00:17:08,528
Well, at least with
this, the toilets

419
00:17:08,570 --> 00:17:10,530
now look a little nicer.

420
00:17:10,572 --> 00:17:11,990
- [Official] Oh,
it really stinks.

421
00:17:12,032 --> 00:17:14,325
- [Official] It smells
like there's a pig in here.

422
00:17:14,367 --> 00:17:15,869
- This may be only
a toilet but it's

423
00:17:15,910 --> 00:17:18,329
still horrible having
one of those roam around

424
00:17:18,371 --> 00:17:19,873
the holy royal court.

425
00:17:21,374 --> 00:17:24,502
- Hmph, speaking of which, have
you heard about that report?

426
00:17:24,544 --> 00:17:25,837
(frustrated groan)

427
00:17:25,879 --> 00:17:27,505
- Yes, it seems like
quite a large amount.

428
00:17:27,547 --> 00:17:30,842
- [Shkrei] I am not going
to let this get me down.

429
00:17:30,884 --> 00:17:32,886
- I feel terrible
having an honored Jougen

430
00:17:32,927 --> 00:17:35,638
such as yourself do stuff
like polish my shoes.

431
00:17:35,680 --> 00:17:38,516
- Don't worry, this is
part of my job, after all.

432
00:17:38,558 --> 00:17:40,310
- But I guess with
the meager lifestyle

433
00:17:40,352 --> 00:17:41,978
of someone from way
out in Koku province,

434
00:17:42,020 --> 00:17:43,563
you'd be used to
this sort of work.

435
00:17:43,605 --> 00:17:45,482
- Of course, you're
absolutely right.

436
00:17:45,523 --> 00:17:47,567
Although I must admit,
I've never polished

