00:17:49,319 --> 00:17:50,403
All right, I'm done!

439
00:17:50,445 --> 00:17:51,279
Ugh!

440
00:17:51,321 --> 00:17:52,364
- Oops, oh, clumsy me.

441
00:17:52,405 --> 00:17:53,740
I lost my balance for a second.

442
00:17:53,782 --> 00:17:55,909
(groans)

443
00:17:57,494 --> 00:17:58,661
- Huh?

444
00:17:58,703 --> 00:18:00,330
- We don't have a
lot of time to waste

445
00:18:00,372 --> 00:18:01,456
so I'll need you to
take care of both of us

446
00:18:01,498 --> 00:18:03,375
at the same time.

447
00:18:03,416 --> 00:18:05,710
- Oh yes, with pleasure, sir.

448
00:18:05,752 --> 00:18:06,878
(gasp)

449
00:18:06,920 --> 00:18:08,004
(chuckle)

450
00:18:08,046 --> 00:18:09,714
- By the way, Official
Waha, what about

451
00:18:09,756 --> 00:18:10,882
that rumor going around?

