00:18:20,600 --> 00:18:21,559
(gasps)

457
00:18:21,601 --> 00:18:23,645
(laughs)

458
00:18:24,604 --> 00:18:25,438
(groans)

459
00:18:25,480 --> 00:18:27,357
- Oh, sorry about that.

460
00:18:27,399 --> 00:18:29,567
- That's all right, sir.

461
00:18:29,609 --> 00:18:31,903
- I leave organizing
these documents up to you.

462
00:18:33,780 --> 00:18:35,365
(gasp)

463
00:18:35,407 --> 00:18:37,575
(determined exhale)

464
00:18:37,617 --> 00:18:39,619
(pants)

465
00:18:40,954 --> 00:18:43,623
- Shu is still cleaning
the palace toilets?

466
00:18:43,665 --> 00:18:45,792
Poor thing, it's been
half a month already.

467
00:18:51,756 --> 00:18:53,717
And despite being a
top-ranking Jougen,

468
00:18:53,758 --> 00:18:56,386
Initiate Tou is still out
there polishing shoes.

469
00:18:56,428 --> 00:18:58,013
- [Kijin] Their
instructor is Official Ro.

470
00:18:58,054 --> 00:18:59,514
It can't be helped.

471
00:18:59,556 --> 00:19:02,600
Those capable of clawing their
way to the top will do so.

472
00:19:02,642 --> 00:19:04,602
Don't concern yourself with it.

473
00:19:04,644 --> 00:19:07,480
That aside, Ykri,
take these documents.

474
00:19:07,522 --> 00:19:08,773
Toilet cleaning
and shoe polishing

475
00:19:08,815 --> 00:19:10,316
duties are in the morning.

476
00:19:10,358 --> 00:19:11,776
I believe they
spend the afternoon

477
00:19:11,818 --> 00:19:14,362
organizing documents
in the archives.

478
00:19:14,404 --> 00:19:15,780
Add these to their pile of work

479
00:19:15,822 --> 00:19:18,575
before either Shkrei
or Recruit Tou arrive.

480
00:19:18,616 --> 00:19:19,451
(gasps)

481
00:19:19,492 --> 00:19:20,660
- How could you?

482
00:19:20,702 --> 00:19:22,746
I'm disappointed in
you, Senior Secretary.

483
00:19:22,787 --> 00:19:24,581
People are already making
things more difficult

484
00:19:24,622 --> 00:19:27,417
for them by giving them
additional work out of spite.

485
00:19:27,459 --> 00:19:28,335
- [Kijin] So?

486
00:19:28,376 --> 00:19:29,044
What of it?

487
00:19:30,378 --> 00:19:31,921
In the meantime, why
don't you come up

488
00:19:31,963 --> 00:19:34,424
with your objections while
you read over these documents?

489
00:19:34,466 --> 00:19:35,884
- Hm?

490
00:19:35,925 --> 00:19:36,760
(gasps)

491
00:19:36,801 --> 00:19:38,053
Then, these are...

492
00:19:38,094 --> 00:19:39,429
- [Kijin] Go.

493
00:19:39,471 --> 00:19:40,430
I've heard enough
of your complaints.

494
00:19:40,472 --> 00:19:41,264
- Yes sir.

495
00:19:44,726 --> 00:19:45,977
- [Shkrei] They say
part of learning

496
00:19:46,019 --> 00:19:47,771
is three years on a rock.

497
00:19:47,812 --> 00:19:49,647
I just have to keep
believing that one day

498
00:19:49,689 --> 00:19:51,358
all of this is gonna pay off.

499
00:19:53,735 --> 00:19:55,987
All right, at last
I'm finished here.

500
00:19:56,029 --> 00:19:57,113
Huh?

501
00:19:57,155 --> 00:19:59,157
Oh hello, you're Hakumei
Heki, aren't you?

502
00:19:59,199 --> 00:19:59,991
(bell chimes)

503
00:20:00,033 --> 00:20:01,785
- Hmph.

504
00:20:01,826 --> 00:20:03,995
- Hey, what's wrong, do
you have a stomachache?

505
00:20:04,037 --> 00:20:05,163
- It's not that.

