00:20:05,205 --> 00:20:06,790
Aren't you even
annoyed by all this?

507
00:20:06,831 --> 00:20:08,166
I mean, come on, you've
been doing nothing

508
00:20:08,208 --> 00:20:10,960
but cleaning these toilets
for half a month now.

509
00:20:11,002 --> 00:20:11,628
- Well...

510
00:20:12,754 --> 00:20:14,005
- [Hakumei] Hm, guess it's true.

511
00:20:14,047 --> 00:20:15,715
Maybe women really
are better suited

512
00:20:15,757 --> 00:20:17,175
for this kind of work.

513
00:20:17,217 --> 00:20:20,512
You're a woman, so why did
you take the national exams?

514
00:20:20,553 --> 00:20:21,680
- [Shkrei] Well, I--

515
00:20:21,721 --> 00:20:23,390
- It's because of
you taking the exam

516
00:20:23,431 --> 00:20:24,766
that I only ranked fourth.

517
00:20:24,808 --> 00:20:27,727
Me, the one hailed by
everyone as a child prodigy.

518
00:20:27,769 --> 00:20:29,813
It's a total embarrassment
to have placed below

519
00:20:29,854 --> 00:20:32,482
someone who is now in
charge of cleaning toilets.

520
00:20:32,524 --> 00:20:34,609
(exhales)

521
00:20:34,651 --> 00:20:35,527
- Hmph.

522
00:20:37,070 --> 00:20:39,489
- [Shkrei] Pardon me, I have
to work in the archives next.

523
00:20:39,531 --> 00:20:40,657
I should probably get going.

524
00:20:40,699 --> 00:20:41,533
- Hm?

525
00:20:42,659 --> 00:20:43,493
Hmph.

526
00:20:43,535 --> 00:20:45,995
(string music)

527
00:20:47,914 --> 00:20:51,084
(curious vocalization)

528
00:20:57,799 --> 00:20:58,633
- Huh?

529
00:20:58,675 --> 00:20:59,884
Mm.

530
00:20:59,926 --> 00:21:01,761
- It must be boring
cleaning the toilets.

531
00:21:01,803 --> 00:21:03,179
That's why I've
agreed to specially

532
00:21:03,221 --> 00:21:04,889
allow you to assist
with my work.

533
00:21:04,931 --> 00:21:07,642
You ought to be grateful
for my generosity.

534
00:21:07,684 --> 00:21:10,186
Make sure everything's done
by tomorrow morning, hm?

535
00:21:11,938 --> 00:21:12,856
- Yes sir.

536
00:21:12,897 --> 00:21:14,190
I'll be sure to have it done.

537
00:21:17,569 --> 00:21:19,446
(sighs)

538
00:21:19,487 --> 00:21:22,907
- You're a woman, so why did
you take the national exams?

539
00:21:22,949 --> 00:21:24,826
(troubled sigh)

540
00:21:24,868 --> 00:21:26,911
- Oh well, I guess I should
try and get some of this

541
00:21:26,953 --> 00:21:28,830
done before Eigetsu gets here.

542
00:21:28,872 --> 00:21:29,831
- Hello, Shkrei.

543
00:21:29,873 --> 00:21:31,166
- Huh?

544
00:21:31,207 --> 00:21:32,167
- Ah, Lord KMyk.

545
00:21:33,084 --> 00:21:34,252
- I was looking for Lord ShMka

546
00:21:34,294 --> 00:21:36,504
but it seems he's not
here at the moment.

547
00:21:36,546 --> 00:21:39,132
Have you finished cleaning
the toilets already?

548
00:21:39,174 --> 00:21:40,050
- Yes.

549
00:21:41,718 --> 00:21:43,595
- Is this part of your work?

550
00:21:43,636 --> 00:21:44,554
- No, it's not.

551
00:21:44,596 --> 00:21:46,097
Mm, yes, it is.

552
00:21:46,139 --> 00:21:48,683
Eigetsu and I agreed
to take on this work.

553
00:21:49,726 --> 00:21:50,643
- I see.

554
00:21:51,603 --> 00:21:52,228
Mm.

555
00:21:59,694 --> 00:22:00,779
Fight your way up.

556
00:22:00,820 --> 00:22:01,946
(gasps)

557
00:22:01,988 --> 00:22:03,907
From here on in, you're
on your own, Shkrei.

558
00:22:03,948 --> 00:22:06,993
Don't expect any more
help from Shkei or myself.

559
00:22:07,035 --> 00:22:08,828
But even so, you
gotta claw your way up

560
00:22:08,870 --> 00:22:10,830
until you reach your goal.

561
00:22:10,872 --> 00:22:12,874
Passing as Tanka as
your age had nothing

562
00:22:12,916 --> 00:22:15,085
to do with my assistance
or Lord ShMka's.

563
00:22:15,126 --> 00:22:17,128
It happened because
you had a strong desire

564
00:22:17,170 --> 00:22:18,505
within your heart.

565
00:22:18,546 --> 00:22:20,215
Otherwise, you never
could've become Tanka

566
00:22:20,256 --> 00:22:22,008
at the age of 17.

567
00:22:22,050 --> 00:22:24,803
There is a place you
wanna get to, isn't there?

568
00:22:24,844 --> 00:22:27,180
(harp music)

569
00:22:29,015 --> 00:22:30,100
- Yes, there is.

570
00:22:32,352 --> 00:22:34,604
- Mm, from now on,
it's that dream

571
00:22:34,646 --> 00:22:36,731
of yours that's gonna support
you and keep you going.

572
00:22:36,773 --> 00:22:38,066
Keep fighting your
way to the top

573
00:22:38,108 --> 00:22:40,151
as if your life depended on it.

574
00:22:40,193 --> 00:22:41,611
We'll be waiting.

575
00:22:41,653 --> 00:22:42,821
(gasps)

576
00:22:42,862 --> 00:22:43,822
- Thank you Lord KMyk.

577
00:22:43,863 --> 00:22:45,865
Thank you for reminding me.

578
00:22:47,742 --> 00:22:48,576
(gasps)

579
00:22:48,618 --> 00:22:49,244
Lord KMyk!

580
00:22:49,285 --> 00:22:50,704
- Ah?

581
00:22:50,745 --> 00:22:52,080
What is it?

582
00:22:52,122 --> 00:22:54,040
It's almost time for lunch
so I'm on my way out.

583
00:22:54,082 --> 00:22:57,752
- Well, you see the
exit, isn't over there.

584
00:22:57,794 --> 00:23:01,715
- (grunts) This mountain of
books is so disorienting!

585
00:23:01,756 --> 00:23:03,967
Why do they insist on having
so many books in here?

586
00:23:04,009 --> 00:23:06,136
Just because it's the archives.

587
00:23:06,177 --> 00:23:09,889
(traditional Japanese music)

588
00:23:11,057 --> 00:23:12,017
- Ah!

589
00:23:12,058 --> 00:23:12,892
Hm.

590
00:23:15,812 --> 00:23:17,897
(snores)

591
00:23:26,072 --> 00:23:27,824
- [KMyk] From now on,
it's that dreams of yours

592
00:23:27,866 --> 00:23:29,826
that's gonna support
you and keep you going.

593
00:23:29,868 --> 00:23:31,161
Keep fighting your
way to the top

594
00:23:31,202 --> 00:23:33,580
as if your life depended on it.

595
00:23:33,621 --> 00:23:35,331
- The one thing that
will always support me

596
00:23:35,373 --> 00:23:37,834
is that dream of mine.

597
00:23:37,876 --> 00:23:41,713
(traditional Japanese music)

598
00:23:46,801 --> 00:23:51,139
{\an8}(peaceful music in
foreign language)

599
00:25:01,835 --> 00:25:03,211
- [Shkrei] Whether
it's toilet cleaning

600
00:25:03,253 --> 00:25:05,839
or shoe polishing, I'll
do whatever I have to.

601
00:25:05,880 --> 00:25:09,217
There's no way I'm gonna give
into harassment like this.

602
00:25:09,259 --> 00:25:10,176
Huh?

603
00:25:10,218 --> 00:25:12,012
Lord KMyk, are you all right?

604
00:25:12,053 --> 00:25:13,888
You look a little
under the weather.

